name bidi
category Package
revision 77682
shortdesc Bidirectional typesetting in plain TeX and LaTeX, using XeTeX or LuaTeX
longdesc A convenient interface for typesetting bidirectional texts with
longdesc plain TeX and LaTeX, using XeTeX or LuaTeX. The package
longdesc includes adaptations for use with many other commonly-used
longdesc packages.
